Package: libatomspace-storage
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libatomspace (>= 5.0.5),
         libcogutil (>= 1.0.0)
Description: OpenCog AtomSpace storage backends (runtime)
 AtomSpace Storage provides pluggable backend storage for the AtomSpace
 hypergraph database, including support for RocksDB, PostgreSQL, and
 other storage engines.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries for runtime use.

Package: libatomspace-storage-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libatomspace-storage (= ${binary:Version}),
         libatomspace-dev (>= 5.0.5),
         libcogutil-dev (>= 1.0.0),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenCog AtomSpace storage backends (development files)
 AtomSpace Storage provides pluggable backend storage for the AtomSpace
 hypergraph database, including support for RocksDB, PostgreSQL, and
 other storage engines.
 .
 This package contains the header files and development libraries.
